genresAdvancedInfo.name: kyrgyz hip hop
genresAdvancedInfo.description: A relatively new genre of music in Kyrgyzstan, Kyrgyz hip hop blends traditional Kyrgyz melodies and rhythms with modern hip hop beats and lyrics. With its unique sound and socially conscious lyrics, Kyrgyz hip hop has become a popular form of expression for young people in Kyrgyzstan, and has helped to promote a sense of cultural pride and identity.
